{"tid":2142560,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"朱凱廸: 以官司限制出境 圖以《國安法》檢控","createTime":"2020-08-06T13:12:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-06T16:03:49.000Z","uid":240362,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"6831a1507467348ab9820613d2e2ed515d2aa288","tid":2142560,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T13:12:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200806/CMFMMEF3EOJ5LLM5GTHOUII6U4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200806%2FCMFMMEF3EOJ5LLM5GTHOUII6U4%2F&d=il%2BrReVPph3FBkDtfLAFOi8EbckYnMoWLUJTUpLSOd8%3D&h=08cab399\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200806%2FCMFMMEF3EOJ5LLM5GTHOUII6U4%2F&h=001858d5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200806/CMFMMEF3EOJ5LLM5GTHOUII6U4/</a><br />\n<br />\n事隔逾兩個月，警方再就今年六四燭光晚會，向多名支聯會主要成員加控「明知而參與未經批准集結」，同時亦以同一罪名檢控黃之鋒、羅冠聰、岑敖暉等抗爭派人士。有學者認為市民會質疑今次檢控是政治打壓，而今次有份被控的朱凱廸認為，警方檢控的目的是令法庭限制被控人士出境，以便作長期打壓。"},{"pid":"b45dbe4fc5c45cc89697456f29c73a1c218b5a1d","tid":2142560,"uid":273703,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T13:13:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b7071de9ccb21e441ea14d41463cce01585f6c88","tid":2142560,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b45dbe4fc5c45cc89697456f29c73a1c218b5a1d","tid":2142560,"uid":273703,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T13:13:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T13:15:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0090bb0eda38c97bc66568a6d67621ba7e87871e","tid":2142560,"uid":232157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,